      "side": 1,
      "message": "Looks good to me.\nThis is for the D-Bus layer; is there interest in adding this to the Redfish layer?\nAs a minor note: OpenBMC service-config-manager can also disable services (like IPMI on UDP port 623) which overlaps part of the firewall port blocking function.",
      "revId": "e8e6b143abe6d3e5ee82f0b4952b532558537aa0",
