      "writtenOn": "2026-06-02T19:54:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This already exists.  Services only bind on the protocols they support.  We likely need to define a way to block ICMP ping (as that\u0027s handled by the kernel), but that\u0027s just another service we add to the list.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 67,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 67,
        "endChar": 66
