      "writtenOn": "2026-06-02T19:54:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "How would this work in Redfish?  This \"firewall\" feature has been proposed multiple times at a DMTF standards level, and every time ran into the problem of not being able to define the use case (same as above) well enough to even come up with a model, or why it\u0027s separate from the things that already exist.\n\n\nIs there more details there on what the Redfish API looks like somewhere?",
